channel.title: Adding a friends list to my server - Help, Please
channel.description:
I would really like to know how to add a friends list to my server source. If you were wondering, I am using Killamess' "Final Devolution" - Mainly because the magic graphics are so good, and the combat (mellee,ranged, magic) is the best I've seen.
Anyway yeah if you could help me with adding a friends list to my source I would very well appreciate it.
Thanks.
